OL,7,FWho invented Butter Chicken? Two rival
OL,8,Frestaurants in India have taken this
OL,9,Fcurry war to court to decided who
OL,10,Ffirst came up with the popular dish
OL,12,FTwo restaurants in India are in the
OL,13,Fmiddle of a legal dispute over the
OL,14,Fright to call themselves the home of
OL,15,Fthe original recipe for butter chicken.
OL,17,FThe dish is one of the most popular
OL,18,Fcurries in the world, made with .
OL,20,FIt is dubbed one of and one of the
OL,21,Fmost popular curries in the UK.
