OL,7,FThe cuisine though is at the centre of
OL,8,Fa legal fight, as the two eateries
OL,9,FDelhi Moti Mahal and Daryaganj both
OL,10,Fclaim they were the first to create it.
OL,12,FThe lawsuit to decide the matter was
OL,13,Fbrought by the family who run Moti
OL,14,FMahal.
