OL,7,FAccording to the Gujral family, the
OL,8,Fdish was the creation of their
OL,9,Fgrandfather Kundan Lal Gujral who
OL,10,Ffounded the restaurant in Peshawar, in
OL,11,Fwhat is now Pakistan.
OL,13,FAfter India was split during partition
OL,14,Fin 1947, they moved the restaurant to
OL,15,FDelhi.
