OL,7,FAs well as seeking rights to the title
OL,8,Fof butter chicken inventor, the Gujral
OL,9,Ffamily is seeking $240,000 in damages.
OL,11,FGiven the slow pace of India's courts,
OL,12,Fthe pressing question of butter
OL,13,Fchicken's origins may not be solved
OL,14,Ffor months or even years.
OL,16,FThe next hearing of the case will be
OL,17,Fin May.
